snippet.title: Old Friends Dog Game - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to Old Friends Dog Sanctuary, where love never grows old! 💛

Old Friends Dog Game is an upcoming game based on the REAL life Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary in Mt. Juliet, Tennessee. It's a game about friendship for people who love dogs. 🐶

Coming to mobile SOON!

Follow: 
🐶 OUR WEBSITE: https://www.oldfriendsgame.com
🐶 FACEBOOK: http://www.facebook.com/oldfriendsgame/ 
🐶 TWITTER:  http://www.twitter.com/PlayOldFriends 
🐶 INSTAGRAM: http://www.instagram.com/oldfriendsgame/

For more updates in the future! 

You can purchase the 2020 Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary calendar with concept art of the game here! https://ofsds.org/shop-to-support-ofsds/?fbclid=IwAR3a9D_oD-ZxTQgKZ3SJbq86spRbg01DqVMYC5ylGDkXLYSrPCipoIsj2Pc#!/2020-OFSDS-Calendar-A-Year-of-Friendship/p/151353545/category=0

All proceeds from the calendar go to Old Friends Senior Dog Sanctuary! 










#dog #games #oldfriendseniordogsanctuary #doggames #mobilegame
